{"tid":254673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵技術員離奇伏屍路軌    MTR稱: 工業意外","createTime":"2017-05-23T11:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T12:09:55.000Z","uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a139ce5382d27aeee6c1267a3ea0252c3a6db6a","tid":254673,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"【11:00】黑箱車到場準備將死者遺體移送殮房。港鐵工會指員工進入路軌進行維修工作，需要遵守安全指引，否則不能擅闖路軌。<br />\n<br />\n【08:10】港鐵車務總監劉天成交代經過，指死者當時與三名同事乘坐工程車由大圍車廠出發，待馬鞍山線收車後，即前往車公廟站，進行日常路軌檢查工作，當時車上有司機、信號員及技術員。惟到達後，同事卻發現身為技術員的死者失去蹤影，之後死者被另一隊工程人員，發現身穿反光衣倒斃近大圍車廠路軌，港鐵對事件感到十分難過，將全面配合警方調查。至於死者為何會離開工程車，以及離奇倒斃路軌，劉則未有交代。<br />\n<br />\n大圍港鐵車廠凌晨2時許發生奪命工業意外，一名資深技術員疑被工程車輾過，重傷倒臥路軌，工友事後發現報警求助。消防員接報到場，發現技術員腰部有傷痕，已明顯死亡，警方用帳篷將死者遺體遮蓋，經初步調查後，相信案件無可疑，將與勞工處跟進意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓高（59歲），加入港鐵28年，據悉，出事時，高被同事發現失去蹤影，遍尋不獲，立即通知控制中心。10多分鐘後，另一隊工程人員於大圍車廠附近的接收軌道，發現一名工人倒斃路軌，經調查後，證實為失蹤的高。港鐵車務總監劉天成，聞訊後由職員陪同到場了解事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170523/photo/bkn-20170523030241631-0523_00822_001_05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170523030241631-0523_00822_001_05b.jpg&h=a87031ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員接報到場。(梁國雄攝)"},{"pid":"d15d808ba46bf998189452d7d144d1009a31a71e","tid":254673,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"離奇伏屍都無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88054d31c4e6951f010419549340786ef493f62b","tid":254673,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f5013f44f3a6773ae40a0f3d0783fb8bcc2a02e","tid":254673,"uid":90443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ec28552556100e2ecfd07975c71c5366751de91","tid":254673,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"對唔住碾撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cec46a3da285549bb2b69da06402bcd48d3a5f","tid":254673,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離奇伏屍都無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拿，人地話無就無。"},{"pid":"55e2f033a45f8607656a3d247df1ceb9ab1d9f42","tid":254673,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>離奇伏屍都無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反正我信了</blockquote><br />\n猶差咁叻，即刻就判斷無可疑"},{"pid":"9b3faed6191f1a9f1778d0d2619d640eb43a80ef","tid":254673,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>離奇伏屍都無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反正我信了</blockquote><br />\n猶差咁叻，即刻就判斷無可疑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少野做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215abde075ee713a790d2ebf9d14f1e49f2bd755","tid":254673,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>離奇伏屍都無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反正我信了</blockquote><br />\n猶差咁叻，即刻就判斷無可疑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少野做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又係 大事化小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}